text: Import is the act of bringing goods into a country. Import may also refer to: *import and export of data, in computing *import tariff, a tax on imported goods *import quota, a type of trade restriction *Import substitution industrialization, an economic policy *Import scene, a subculture that centers on modifying imported brand cars *The #Import directive in Objective-C *The import keyword in Java ==See also== * Export (disambiguation)
title: Import (disambiguation)
